  "text": "• Empirical results of [CITATION_1] elucidate a large degree of nonlinearity for sites with V S30 Ͻ 180 m / s, while nonlinearity rapidly diminishes with increasing V S30 . To be more specific, linear site amplification starts dominating beyond V S30 of 300 m / s.",
